data.description: This is a charming Beacon Hill cottage that has some very nice improvements for the new owner. The house was totally rewired in 2011, freshly painted inside and out, new flooring installed. The home is move in ready. There are three nice bedrooms and two baths, a wonderful front porch Brokered And Advertised By: Phyllis Browning Company Listing Agent: Ann Van Pelt
